nt-family: 宋体; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"">【灶火农家菜】</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">；</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">19：00&nbsp;&nbsp;前往郴州市唯一的外资国际奢华品牌白金五星级酒店---温德姆至尊豪廷大酒店（车程约20分钟）；</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">20：00&nbsp;&nbsp;抵达温德姆至尊豪廷大酒店，办理入住手续后自由活动，自由享受27度恒温泳池、健身房等酒店各类免费配套设施。</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-indent: 384px; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">住宿：郴州市白金五星温德姆至尊豪廷大酒店双人间</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-weight: bold; font-size: 12px;""><br/></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-weight: bold; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"">第二天（2月18日大年初三）：酒店--东江湖景区--入住酒店</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">07：30&nbsp;自由享受酒店精美自助早餐；</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">09：30&nbsp;集合前往</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"">【东江湖景区】</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">（车程约30分钟）；</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">10：00&nbsp;抵达东江湖景区换乘景交车游览</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"">【东江湖景区】</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">（已含门票+船票+景交车,全天游览），国家AAAA级旅游区，被誉为“湘南洞庭，东方瑞士”，东江湖融山的隽秀、水的神韵于一体，挟南国秀色、禀历史文明于一身，被誉为“人间天上一湖水，万千景象在其中”，进入景区可看到东江大坝、猴骨山瀑布，接着前往码头乘船游览东江湖，您可以近距离欣赏东江湖美景、体验游湖之乐</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-style: italic; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px;"">。</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">12：30&nbsp;&nbsp;前往餐厅享用</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"">【三文鱼宴】</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">；</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">14：00&nbsp;&nbsp;游览【龙景大峡谷瀑布群】，龙景峡谷是一处集旅游观光、休闲康健的综合性旅游景区，峡谷全线游程约为1公里，沿途山势陡峭、青山滴翠，青潭、瀑布成群，是我国目前瀑布密集度较高的景区；</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">15：00&nbsp;&nbsp;自由活动，自行返回酒店，自由乘景区车前往4号桥，开始徒步醉美【小东江】景区段，偶遇雾漫美景，小东江的水质达到国家一级饮用水标准，干净、清澈的湖水，直接渗透我们的心灵。两岸常年的峰峦叠翠、土房、红叶、白云等自然景观形成倒影，美丽绝伦。在如画的风景里沿游步道行走约2公里，抵达2号桥处，安排&nbsp;仿十大美图【江山渔者·烟波泛】布置撒网、捕鱼场景，供拍照留影。行程所到之处，空气中、水中都弥漫着纯净【小编无法用言语来形容此景，简单的呐喊“干净，原来可以这么美丽”】；</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">19：00&nbsp;于酒店餐厅享用晚餐；</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">20：00&nbsp;自由活动，自由享受27度恒温泳池、健身房等酒店各类免费配套设施；</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-indent: 396px; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">住宿：郴州市白金五星温德姆至尊豪廷大酒店双人间</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-weight: bold; font-size: 12px;""><br/></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-weight: bold; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"">第三天（2月19日大年初四）：酒店--仰天湖大草原--入住酒店</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">07：30&nbsp;享受酒店精美自助早餐；</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">08：30&nbsp;集合出发前往</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"">【仰天湖大草原】</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">（车程约1.5小时）；</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">10：00&nbsp;抵达后游览</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"">【仰天湖大草原】</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">（已含门票，游览2.5小时）,仰天湖为第四纪冰川期馈赠的一个死火山口，其自然水泊面积20余亩，海拨高度1350米，是悬系于长江、珠江分水线与京珠高速十字交点旁的一颗璀璨明珠，亦为自由旅人作家誉为“地球上（北江之源）的一滴眼泪。仰天湖大草原也有千姿百态、鬼斧神工的安源石林和凝写苍桑、流云漫锁的平头山寨;还涵盖有十里杜鹃、雾海重田、高山观日、晴雪云耕、通天洞峡、滴水岱瀑等十大景观；</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">12：30&nbsp;&nbsp;享用</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"">【</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"">仰天湖</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"">农家菜】</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">；</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">13：30&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"">集合前往广东省韶关市的</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"">丽宫国际旅游度假区</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"">（车程约2.5小时）。</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"">16：00&nbsp;&nbsp;抵达</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"">乳源丽宫国际旅游度假区，办理入住手续；</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"">18：00&nbsp;&nbsp;于酒店餐厅享用晚餐；</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"">19：00&nbsp;&nbsp;凭房卡自由浸泡</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"">乳源丽宫国际旅游度假区的【</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"">云瑶谷温泉</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"">】</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"">(每张房卡限2次)，云瑶谷温泉源自千年喷涌的青岗温泉，其周边山峦叠翠，丛林密布，地层水网交错，泉水</span><a href=""http://baike.baidu.com/view/70033.htm""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"">取之不尽，用之不竭</span></a><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"">，是名副其实的富水源，且泉水清澈，水温恒定保持70℃。故泉源常年热浪蒸腾，泉汽氤氲，云瑶谷温泉水质经地质矿产部检测鉴定，为国内罕见的弱碱性“偏硅酸锶泉”，且含有大量铜、钴、钥、硒、铁、锌等多种对人体有益的微量元素。因此可达到有病治病、无病强身健体的功效，长居于此，延年益寿，云瑶谷温泉是名副其实的养生温泉。</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">住宿：五星标准乳源丽宫国际温泉酒店双人间</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"">或同级</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><br/></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-weight: bold; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"">第四天（2月20日大年初五）：酒店---云门山玻璃桥---深圳</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">07：30&nbsp;享受酒店自助早餐。</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">08：30&nbsp;集合出发前往【云门山旅游度假区】</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"">（车程30分钟）。</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">09：00&nbsp;开始游览【云门山旅游度假区】(已含大门票+玻璃桥门票，如需乘坐缆车自理,游览约3小时)，云门山自然风景区依托云门山得天独厚的自然风景资源，发挥云门寺佛教文化胜地和“世界过山瑶之乡”的优势，突出体现“云门禅宗文化”及“过山瑶民俗风情文化”的特色主题。云门山旅游度假区是按照国家5A标准打造的综合性旅游景区；</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">10：30&nbsp;&nbsp;走上【云门山玻璃桥】【云门山玻璃桥首次对外开放，此时会出现人多拥挤，排队等候的现象，请各贵宾稍安勿躁，有自序的排队等候】；云门山玻璃桥是目前广东省规模最大的全透明高空景观玻璃桥，桥面全部采用透明玻璃铺设，桥体全长316米，垂直高度达168米，玻璃桥位于云门山自然风景区内，悬于望君台直通对面山峰，两峰地势险峻，中间峡谷横穿，行走其上彷如“人在空中走，景在脚下游”，惊险无比；云深雾重之际，桥上悬空赏景漫步云端，如若“脚踏祥云，腾云驾雾”，置身于峡谷天堑以独特角度感受云门山之美景；</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">12：30&nbsp;&nbsp;享用午餐；</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">13：30&nbsp;&nbsp;结束四天愉快的行程，集合返回深圳（</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">车程约4小时</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">）；</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">18：00&nbsp;&nbsp;抵深圳后交对讲机，</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"">自行返回深圳温馨的家！</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><br/></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: nor