ial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">领航领队：深圳出发的专业领航车、全程领航员、随团领队、各地专业导游服务。</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">旅游保险：十万元/人的旅行社责任险、十万元/人的旅游人身意外险。</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">其它费用：自驾路书，车标。</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"">【收费</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"">未含</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"">】</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">全程路桥费、全程油费、全程</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">停车费、单房差1000元及个人行程外支出；</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"">【</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"">特别提醒</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"">】</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">所有团友在出发时都必须带上身份证，老人请带上身份证、退休证、老年证，小童请带上户口本、身份证、学生证等。</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-weight: bold; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 102, 0); text-decoration: underline;"">【特别提示】每逢节日均为</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 102, 0); text-decoration: underline;"">旅游旺季，如遇旅行社不可控制因素（如塌方、塞车、天气、车辆故障等原因）导致无法按约定行程游览及各景点、餐厅游客较多，可能会出现拥挤、排队等候等现象，我社尽努力协调，旅行社有权根据实际情况对行程游览先后顺序作出合理调整，旅行社负责协助解决或退还未产生的门票款，由此产生的其它费用游客自理，旅行社不承担由此造成的损失及责任，因此给您带来的不便敬请谅解。</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><br/></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">酒店介绍：</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-weight: bold; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"">第一</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"">/</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"">二晚：郴州市温德姆至尊豪廷大酒店（</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"">白金五星）</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">郴州温德姆至尊豪廷大酒店是由美国温德姆酒店管理集团经营管理，是目前湖南省郴州市唯一一家外资国际奢华品牌白金五星级酒店。酒店紧邻风景名胜苏仙岭、万华岩、飞天山及东江湖等旅游观光胜地，酒店楼高82.5米，共23层，拥有各种舒适的客房及套房390间套，每间客房都为宾客精心设计，各项配套设施齐全，是商务和休闲宾客的首选，位于酒店3楼的康体娱乐中心配备了一系列完善的康体休闲设施，能让您在这里彻底放松身心！！</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><img src=""http://l.b2b168.com/2018/01/12/09/201801120950041119634.jpg"" title="""" alt="""" style=""width: 683.067px; height: 152.333px;""/></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-weight: bold; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"">第三晚：乳源丽宫国际温泉酒店</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">乳源丽宫国际温泉酒店位于世界过山瑶之乡——乳源，是国家4A级旅游景区，这里占地面积近千亩，有丽宫国际温泉酒店、凤凰山森林度假别墅、卧龙岭生态旅游观光区、开心农场、产权别墅等，客房典雅大方，环境清雅舒适。会议中心有可同时容纳600人会议的会议厅及中、小型会议室12间，配备外语同声传译系统，宴会中心有可同时容纳近千人的宴会大厅及各式风味厅6个、VIP包间15间、烛光湖畔风味宵夜廊，沐足按摩、棋牌、健身美容、SPA水疗、夜总会、网吧、乒乓球室、桌球室等配套服务一应俱全。云瑶谷温泉区主要为SPA室内养神区、禅境养心岛、五道养生谷、森林养性坡，还有冷热水大型冲浪沙滩项目——山谷夏威夷海滩，可以媲美迪拜帆船酒店的“疯狂山泉水世界”。</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><img src=""http://l.b2b168.com/2018/01/12/09/201801120950043434904.jpg"" title="""" alt="""" style=""width: 683.067px; height: 153px;""/></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">自驾游需知：</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">四、停车场的车辆停放，“重要物品可不要放在车上啦”</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">因为我们车队车辆较多，很多地方的停车场面积不够，在车辆停放过程中，请各位车主朋友们全力配合工作人员的指挥啦``在停放过程或等候进入停车场的过程中，也许时间稍稍长一点儿，大家请不要按喇叭，以良好的姿态展示我们车主们的优秀素质啦``如果您停放时缺少一点点儿把握，请随时通知我们工作人员代您进行停放啦```</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><br/></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">五、住宿安排</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">1、由工作人员发放房卡；</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">2、领取房卡时请报上房间号；</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">3、退房时可不要遗忘物品的（充电器、手机、钱包、浴具等）；</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">4、有些酒店的物品赔偿好贵啊！`相信我们都能保重~</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><br/></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">温馨提示：&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">01、出发前请务必将您的爱车加满油、备好维修工具、检查备胎气压等；</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">02、车辆请购买交强险，车辆保险、第三者责任保险提高到50-100万</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">03、出省旅游，请带齐车辆行驶证、驾驶证及有效进关证件等；</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">04、根据自己喜欢配备CD、MP3音乐同路途上的一切使用物品；</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">05、全程所有油费、路桥费、停车费用由车主自己支付；&nbsp;</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">06、</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">敬请爱护和保管好我们配发给您的车载对讲机，如有损坏遗失，需造价赔偿！</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">07、天气情况多变，请携带好雨具，风衣，泳衣，太阳镜，护肤品；</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">08、有些路段行驶时间较长，请为小孩准备零食，饮料；</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">09、</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"">因节假日均</span><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">为出游高峰期，行程和住房安排顺序以实际为准；</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">10、由于不可控制和抗力因素，造成行程的滞留和一切损失，我社不承担任何责任，（如：塞车、景点排队等）；</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">11、自费项目遵循客人自愿消费的原则；</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">12、带上相机和足够内存的SD卡，那里景色优美，会“谋杀”大量内存卡；</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><span style=""font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"">13、记得，带上一份轻松愉快的好心情是必不可少的哦！</span></p><p style=""margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; font-family: 楷体_gb2312; font-size: 12px;""><br/></p><p style=""margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;""><br/></p><p><br cla